THIS IS THE BODY NOW

Gold prices have fluctuated, hitting some price earlier this week. Even as the yellow metal has pulled back from those highs in the last two sessions, someone expects these dips to arise as buying opportunities for investors.

Gold started the year "and it hasn't looked back," someone said. "While the first six weeks of 2016 were to develop, the Fed's inability to secure more rate hikes, or even convince the market they were coming , fueled the rally we are seeing," he added.
